Career Opportunities           U.S. & Canada





Geothermal Turbine Technician - Reno, NV USA 22 July, 2017


Assist Mechanical Engineers in the maintenance and repair the energy converter turbine unit in an Organic Ranking Cycle (ORC) geothermal binary power plant, including disassembly and reassembly.  Working with Mechanical Engineers, perform turbine balancing and alignment, including magnetic level for the pumps, motors and rotors.  Overhaul, repair and maintain pumps and air compressor pumps.  Manage all aspects of outage management, forced outage response and operational surveillance for turbines.  Position may include additional duties that use the required skills. (REQ1496)
For more information or to apply click here




Plant Operator I - Austin, NV USA 18 July, 2017


The primary responsibility of a Plant Operator is to ensure that the operation of the power plant is safely and efficiently carried out in accordance with plant safety procedures and standard operating procedures. (REQ1495)
For more information or to apply click here




Roustabout - Reno NV, USA 15 July, 2017


Duties vary and will be determined by Transportation & Yard Supervisor on a daily basis and Rig Supervisor when assigned. (REQ1463)
For more information or to apply click here




