This position is responsible for installing, testing, maintaining, troubleshooting, and repairing low and high voltage electrical equipment. (REQ1493/REQ1494)
For more information or to apply click here




Logistics Technician - Fernley, NV USA 10 July, 2017


This position is responsible for maintaining the warehouse, inventory control and quoting required equipment necessary to maintain warehouse setting.  Service and maintain warehouse lifting equipment. Recognize, track and organize rig equipment received to and shipped from the warehouse.  Assist and support the Logistics Supervisor in all duties and replace in his or her absence as needed. (REQ1492)
For more information or to apply click here




Logistics Supervisor - Fernley, NV USA 10 July, 2017


This position is responsible for supervising and coordinating the Warehouse Technician, Roustabouts and daily warehouse operations, transportation activities and work flow.  Responsible for the fleet of vehicles, heavy equipment and trailers. (REQ1491)
For more information or to apply click here





Project Engineer - Philadelphia, PA USA 10 July, 2017


This position is responsible for field engineering site surveys, implementation design, equipment selection, project implementations, and data validation for Demand Response and Energy Storage.(REQ1490)
