Solutions



With over five decades of accumulated knowledge and experience, Ormat is today's only vertically integrated geothermal company. Being at the forefront of the geothermal industry, our expertise encompasses the widest range of renewable energy solutions from geothermal power plants to recovered energy, and solar. From designing to developing, building, manufacturing, owning and operating geothermal and recovered energy-based power plants, Ormat sets the industry standard for high quality, simplicity, low maintenance and reliability. 
All of our plants and equipment are uniquely tailored to the site, geothermal resource and ambient conditions. Our solutions offer all of our customers:
 

A single point of responsibility
Full control over the delivery time and cost
Unsurpassed, field-proven knowledge and experience
Simplicity
Flexibility
Unmanned options for operation and maintenance of all our solutions

See a range of Ormat videos and learn more about us and our power plants

Ormat is renowned for our comprehensive knowledge base and technology leadership for the following solutions:

 








Geothermal Power


