Ormat Technologies - Wikipedia






















 






Ormat Technologies

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


Ormat Technologies Inc.


An Ormat 20MW binary power plant at Steamboat, Nevada, USA.




